'''''Art Electric''''' is the third full-length album by Canadian rock band [[The Hunters (band)|The Hunters]]. The album will be released on May 13, 2014 on [[Stomp Records]], Black Numbers, Flix Records.

The foursome reached out to its fans in 2013 to help them fund their album using [[crowdfunding]] platform [[Indiegogo]].

The album was recorded by Matt Allison at Atlas Studios in Chicago.

